
    <h1>Introduction to Handlebars</h1>
    
    <p>Handlebars is a popular templating engine that allows you to create dynamic HTML templates with minimal logic. It's simple to use and provides powerful features for creating reusable and maintainable templates.</p>

    <h2>Key Features of Handlebars</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Simple syntax for creating dynamic content</li>
        <li>Ability to create reusable template partials</li>
        <li>Support for custom helpers to extend functionality</li>
        <li>Conditional statements and loops</li>
        <li>Automatic HTML escaping for security</li>
    </ul>

